INSTALLATION
------------
Make sure you habe installed cmake, libpng, libjpeg, giflib, libxml2, libgmp, libsndfile and libgsl.

libstego
--------
To compile libstego from source-archive extract the libstego-0.90.tar.bz2 and run there

> cmake -DBUILD_LIBSTEGO:BOOL=ON -DBUILD_LIBSTEGOFILE:BOOL=OFF -DBUILD_BINDINGS:BOOL=OFF .
> make

To install libstego run

> make install

as root.

libstegofile
------------
To compile libstegofile from source-archive extract the libstegofile-0.90.tar.bz2 to the same directory as ibstego-0.90.tar.bz2 and run there

> cmake -DBUILD_LIBSTEGO:BOOL=OFF -DBUILD_LIBSTEGOFILE:BOOL=ON -DBUILD_BINDINGS:BOOL=OFF .
> make

To install libstego run

> make install

as root.

python-bindings
---------------
To compile the python bindings from source-archive extract the libstego-python-0.90.tar.bz2 to the same directory as ibstego-0.90.tar.bz2 libstegofile-0.90.tar.bz2 and and run there

> cmake -DBUILD_LIBSTEGO:BOOL=OFF -DBUILD_LIBSTEGOFILE:BOOL=OFF -DBUILD_BINDINGS:BOOL=ON .
> make

To install libstego run

> make install

as root.